        {
          "id": "7f1e42ae4f92_25",
          "href": null,
          "name": "3a94",
          "text": "The Community Currency Knowledge Gateway offers up-to-date information on a wide variety of local and regional currencies. Demurrage has proven a useful currency design feature with a number of regional currencies. Using the stamp script method regional currencies like the German ‘Chiemgauer’, ‘Freicoin’ and ‘Abeille’ in France, and the ‘Waldviertler’ in Austria have shown that money circulates faster in the local economy if demurrage is applied.",
